transforms.code:
WeekEnd = self.params.WeekEndDate
	date = value
	DateList = []
	while date != WeekEnd:
		formated_date = system.date.format(date,'yyyy-MM-dd')
		DateList.append(formated_date)
		date = system.date.addDays(date, 1)
	DateList.append(system.date.format(WeekEnd,'yyyy-MM-dd'))
	return DateList

config.script:
data = self.props.selection.data
	selected_row = self.props.selection.selectedRow
	selected_col = self.props.selection.selectedColumn
	locationList = self.view.custom.locationList
	if selected_col in locationList:
		eventName = (data[0][selected_col]).split('-color-')[0]
		if eventName != None and eventName != ' ':
			result = system.db.runPrepQuery("select id from [participant].[Events] where name = '" + str(eventName)  + "'")
			eventId = result.getValueAt(0,0)
			tab_id = 2 # registration
			system.perspective.navigate("Events/Detail/" + str(eventId) + "/" + str(tab_id))
